text: Sten Bengt Gustaf Gustafsson (2 December 1933 – 15 March 2019) was a Swedish Army general. He was the Supreme Commander of the Swedish Armed Forces from 1986 to 1994. He was born in Hästveda, Sweden. Gustafsson died in his home in Stockholm on 15 March 2019, aged 85. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Swedish military people Category:Generals
